        {
            "title": "美國貿易代表：將在數周或數月內與部分東南亞國家敲定貿易協議",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國貿易代表賈米森·格裡爾表示，華盛頓預計將在幾周內與一些東南亞國家敲定貿易協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">格裡爾周三在吉隆坡舉行的東協經濟部長會議間隙表示：「川普總統和我本人對我們圍繞這些協議共同開展的工作感到自豪，預計將在未來數月甚至是數周內敲定部分協議。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這是自8月所謂對等關稅實施以來，東協與美國首次舉行高級別會議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US to Finalize Asean Trade Deals in Weeks or Months, Greer Says</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e1a91b4a-3590-38ce-8339-b18e5e3e8f0e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8-%E5%B0%87%E5%9C%A8%E6%95%B8%E5%91%A8%E6%88%96%E6%95%B8%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E8%88%87%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%9E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E6%95%B2%E5%AE%9A%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-071024922.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-24 16:35:41",
