        },
        {
            "title": "美團投資的人工智能機器人公司梅卡曼德據悉計畫在香港上市",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 根據知情人士，美團投資的梅卡曼德機器人計畫在香港首次公開募股(IPO)，擬籌資約2億美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士表示，這家美團投資的人工智能機器人公司正在與顧問合作，並以保密形式已提交上市申請。因信息尚未公開，要求匿名的知情人士補充道，發行規模等細節尚未最終確定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:梅卡曼德;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/梅卡曼德\">梅卡曼德</a>將加入其他在香港上市的人工智能相關公司行列。中國科技公司正在加大投入，爭奪人工智能領域的領先地位。恒生科技指數本月早些時候創下四年來最高水平，截至周三今年已上漲41%。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e2bba396-2483-3301-95d3-da43f3df2ece-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博新聞社此前報導，人工智能初創企業智譜考慮在香港上市，華沿機器人也計畫在香港上市。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">梅卡曼德未回應置評請求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">梅卡曼德成立於2016年，產品包括工業級3D相機，以及用於機器人的人工智能軟件，可幫助自動執行諸如上下料、裝配和質檢等任務。2021年完成由美團領投的C輪融資。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Meituan-Backed AI Robotics Firm Mech-Mind Is Said to Plan HK IPO</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%98%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E6%A9%9F%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%A2%85%E5%8D%A1%E6%9B%BC%E5%BE%B7%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E5%9C%A8%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82-070731615.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-24 16:35:43",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "颱風樺加沙｜新「凍資王」紫金黃金國際延遲截飛　孖展申購額暫逾4200億",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/P22ioN7tDq5j5BhIXO8bmg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/am730_578/f09917f9d6541200b5429531b64cb05c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>颱風樺加沙襲港，天文台在今日凌晨2時20分改發十號信號。原定在今日截飛的紫金黃金國際(2259)公布，因惡劣天氣影響，全球發售時間表，招股截止日期將由今日(24日)延至明日(25日)，上市時間由原定下周一(29日)延至周二(30日)。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>此股今次計劃發售3.49億股股份，香港公開發售佔10%，其餘為國配，採用制度B，集資最多250億元，是今次繼寧德時代後的第二大新股。截至發稿，各大券商數據，孖展申購超171倍，孖展申購額4,286億元。</span></span></span></span></span></p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0aafa0ce-d674-3dbf-b1cf-d73f4965aabe-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>此外，原定今日截飛的西普尼亦表示，將改為明天「截飛」，預期定價日為周五(26日)，下周二(30日)掛牌。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/颱風樺加沙-新-凍資王-紫金黃金國際延遲截飛-孖展申購額暫逾4200億/602416?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/颱風樺加沙-新-凍資王-紫金黃金國際延遲截飛-孖展申購額暫逾4200億/602416?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/颱風樺加沙-新-凍資王-紫金黃金國際延遲截飛-孖展申購額暫逾4200億/602416?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A2%B1%E9%A2%A8%E6%A8%BA%E5%8A%A0%E6%B2%99-%E6%96%B0-%E5%87%8D%E8%B3%87%E7%8E%8B-%E7%B4%AB%E9%87%91%E9%BB%83%E9%87%91%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E5%BB%B6%E9%81%B2%E6%88%AA%E9%A3%9B-%E5%AD%96%E5%B1%95%E7%94%B3%E8%B3%BC%E9%A1%8D%E6%9A%AB%E9%80%BE4200%E5%84%84-042800549.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-24 12:40:40",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "花旗退出美債曲線交易 針對聯儲會獨立性的疑慮降溫",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— 花旗策略師退出了一項交易建議：該建議押注隨著對<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>的攻擊加劇，長期美債將表現不佳；他們宣稱，聯儲會上周幾乎一致的政策決定「在一定程度上」減少了外界對該央行獨立性的疑慮。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Dirk Willer和Adam Pickett等策略師建議客戶，在該交易達到「回調上限」(drawdown limit)後，對30年利率遠期將低於5年期利率的押注「獲利了結」。他們在5月以40個基點啟動了這筆交易，8月份在72個基點加碼，之後在60個基點退出。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d825c15d-acc1-3ef2-bca9-f81a8ab8bc63-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">四個月前的建議是基於總統唐納德·川普標誌性的稅收和支出法案將導致政府債務膨脹，令長債承壓。8月底，川普試圖罷免聯儲會理事麗莎·庫克，引發外界擔心政治干預將危及聯儲會對抗通膨的信譽之際，他們加大了押注力度。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YofBaZNZSPUASAG7WReS4Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/47f0a8d82df45b8a2584907381f4ad97\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">令一些市場參與者感到意外的是，在上周的政策會議上，聯儲會會主席杰羅姆·鮑威爾戮力達成近乎一致的共識，支持降息四分之一個百分點。川普任命的理事米蘭是唯一投票支持更大幅度降息的人。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">花旗策略師寫道，自5月啟動貿易談判以來，供應擔憂已變得更加緩和。他們表示，本月的聯儲會政策會議「在一定程度上減輕了人們對聯儲會獨立性的疑慮」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Citigroup Exits Treasuries Curve Trade as Fears Over Fed Subside</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8A%B1%E6%97%97%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E7%BE%8E%E5%82%B5%E6%9B%B2%E7%B7%9A%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93-%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E6%80%A7%E7%9A%84%E7%96%91%E6%85%AE%E9%99%8D%E6%BA%AB-010533956.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-24 11:20:40",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "彭博新聞午間分享 你會想知道的五件事",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">加大投入</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">晶片股在陸港兩地上漲，中芯國際A股與H股雙雙創盤中紀錄新高，此前華為稱計畫三年內在AI晶片領域超越輝達。阿里巴巴亦強勁走升，該公司CEO吳泳銘表示將增加人工智能基礎設施投資。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">仍須謹慎</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會主席鮑威爾稱就業市場和通膨前景面臨風險，重申在權衡進一步降息時可能面臨艱難抉擇。三位聯儲會官員贊成對通膨目標設定區間的想法，而不是目前維持的2%硬性目標。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">猛力抨擊</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">川普在聯合國大會發表了一場充滿怨憤的演講，嚴厲批評聯合國除了「空話」之外毫無建樹，並將氣候變化描述為「一場騙局」。此外，會場接連發生電梯故障、提詞器失靈等小狀況也讓川普不滿，特勤局據悉對此事展開調查。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-a0dd2cf8-cf84-31be-9ea4-2530c766d56c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"川普在聯合國大會發表演講Source: Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/v1PR0xoZThMWScnZ1nq59Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/642f11b9adaa87111edbf45260fcf469\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">川普在聯合國大會發表演講Source: Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">下調目標</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國商飛據悉將C919飛機今年的交貨目標大幅下調了三分之二，目前計畫今年交付約25架。此外，中國商務部周三上午召開新聞發布會，副部長李成鋼稱中國在世貿組織當前和未來談判中，將不再尋求新的特殊和差別待遇。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">巨額融資</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">全球最大穩定幣的發行商Tether Holdings SA目前正在與投資者洽談融資高達200億美元，這筆交易可能會推動這家加密貨幣公司躋身全球價值最高的非上市公司之列。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E5%8D%88%E9%96%93%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E4%BD%A0%E6%9C%83%E6%83%B3%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%B6%E4%BA%8B-044659613.html",
